/*!
\mainpage Overview

\section parameter_handler Parameter Handler
This library provides a tool for changing parameters of different types at runtime.
The parameter_handler allows you to
<ul>
  <li> Define minimal, maximal and default values for a parameter </li>
  <li> Change paramters from everywhere in the application </li>
  <li> Use eigen matrices as parameters </li>
</ul>
The ROSÂ implementation additionally features:
<ul>
  <li> Set and get parameter via ros service </li>
  <li> Using MultiArray messages for full matrix support</li>
  <li> Rqt Plugin to manipulate/tune parameters </li>
</ul>

